</div>
			<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">Christopher Erb</h1>
									<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
									<div id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>
								<div id="contentSub"></div>
												<div id="jump-to-nav" class="mw-jump">
					Jump to:					<a href="#mw-head">navigation</a>, 					<a href="#p-search">search</a>
				</div>
				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><table class="infobox biography vcard" style="width:22em">
<tr>
<th colspan="2" style="text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold"><span class="fn">Christopher Erb</span></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<th scope="row">Born</th>
<td><span style="display:none">(<span class="bday">1972-06-19</span>)</span> June 19, 1972 <span class="noprint ForceAgeToShow">(age&#160;43)</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th scope="row">Residence</th>
<td class="label">Calabasas, CA</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th scope="row">Alma&#160;mater</th>
<td><a href="/wiki/University_of_Washington" title="University of Washington">University of Washington</a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th scope="row">Occupation</th>
<td class="role">Founder, Managing Partner</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th scope="row">Employer</th>
<td class="org">tripleclix</td>
</tr>
</table>
<p><b>Christopher Erb</b> (born June 19, 1972) was the Vice President of Brand Marketing at <a href="/wiki/EA_Sports" title="EA Sports">EA SPORTS</a><sup id="cite_ref-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-1"><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup> and the Executive Vice President of Brand Marketing at <a href="/wiki/Legendary_Pictures" title="Legendary Pictures">Legendary Pictures</a>.<sup id="cite_ref-2" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-2"><span>[</span>2<span>]</span></a></sup> Erb is currently the Managing Partner of tripleclix.</p>
<p></p>
<div id="toc" class="toc">
